          "description": "The way our war heroes are treated at this Veterans Hospital is shameful. From the moment you walk in, the people who are supposed to help with the wheelchairs are terribly inattentive and rude. They talk badly about the doctors and nurses who are actually the ones who do the work. And don't even get me started on the receptionists\u2014they're detestable and ignore the patients. No veteran wants to go to this hospital.",
